  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      In this research study we want to test how people understand a visual scene when the same&#xD;
      image is presented to both the eyes, but portions of these images are altered in terms of&#xD;
      contrast, depth or in some cases motion.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
